Package org.odpi.openmetadata.repositoryservices.rest.server.spring

Class LocalRepositoryServicesResource

java.lang.Object
org.odpi.openmetadata.repositoryservices.rest.server.spring.LocalRepositoryServicesResource
@RestController @RequestMapping("/servers/{serverName}/open-metadata/repository-services/users/{userId}") public class LocalRepositoryServicesResource extends Object
LocalRepositoryServicesResource provides the server-side support for the OMRS Repository REST Services API that are directed to the local repository.
